# Map Features

This directory contains Gherkin feature files for Map interface examples.

## Planned Features

- HashMap operations
- LinkedHashMap (insertion order)
- TreeMap (sorted by key)
- EnumMap (optional)

## Structure

Each feature file should follow the pattern:
```
# language: es

Característica: [Feature description]
  Como desarrollador Java
  Quiero [objective]
  Para [benefit]

  Escenario: [Scenario description]
    Dado [precondition]
    Cuando [action]
    Entonces [expected result]
```

## Notes

- All features should be written in neutral Spanish
- Include comprehensive scenarios covering edge cases
- Focus on demonstrating Map-specific behaviors (key uniqueness, iteration, etc.)
